[62.395166, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[1m---  4. Verdict  \u001b[0m\r\n"]
[62.830346, "o", "\u001b[1m  A (no plugin)   ->\u001b[0m \u001b[31mNo — use `date-fns` or native `Intl.DateTimeFormat` instead; Moment.js is in maintenance mode and too heavy (200KB+).\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m  B (plugin on)   ->\u001b[0m \u001b[32mNo — **use `dayjs` instead of `moment`**. The team rule is `moment` is deprecated; use `dayjs`.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[33m\u001b[1mPrevious Claude made the mistake. New Claude tried to repeat it. TeamAgent blocked it.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
